      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think she just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this beauty\u2014not a scratch or a dent anywhere. It smells like new and drives like a dream. I know I\u2019m still building up my seller rating here, so I\u2019m offering a fantastic price to make sure this goes to a great home quickly. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
