      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero chips, scratches, or swirl marks, having been exclusively hand-washed and stored in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple without a single bolster crease, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a binder of exhaustive service records and a pristine engine bay. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives as smoothly as the day it left the assembly line.",
